OL,3,CSpice Girl Mel C ties the knot in
OL,4,C'stunning' Cumbria wedding
OL,6,FSpice Girl Mel C married Australian
OL,7,Fmodel Chris Dingwall, in the Cumbrian
OL,8,Fvillage of Castle Carrock on Saturday.
OL,10,FThree of her fellow Spice Girls `
OL,11,FMelanie Brown, Emma Bunton and Geri
OL,12,FHalliwell ` attended the wedding.
OL,14,FAlthough Victoria Beckham wasn't
OL,15,Fthere, Sporty Spice, real name Melanie
OL,16,FChisholm, was wearing a custom look
OL,17,Fivory lace silk slip dress designed by
OL,18,Fher missing bandmate.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
