OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1784657907
OL,3,CSpice Girl Mel C ties the knot in
OL,4,C'stunning' Cumbria wedding
OL,6,FDingwell, who wore a black tuxedo,
OL,7,Fproposed to her while the pair were on
OL,8,Fholiday in Mallorca in July 2025.
OL,10,FShe said although she did not see it
OL,11,Fcoming, or ever plan to have a big
OL,12,Fwedding, when he proposed she felt it
OL,13,Fwas "right".
OL,15,FThe 52-year-old told British Vogue,
OL,16,Fwhich had exclusive access to the
OL,17,Fwedding day: "I've had this awakening
OL,18,Fin my 50s ` I'm very comfortable in my
OL,19,Fskin.
OL,26,@uD@EOUuD@KO]yD@NOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
