OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F324A1784657907
OL,3,CSpice Girl Mel C ties the knot in
OL,4,C'stunning' Cumbria wedding
OL,6,F"I thought, you know what, this is a
OL,7,Fpart of my story. When you're my age
OL,8,Fyou're like... I actually want to
OL,9,Fexperience all of the things."
OL,11,FThe UK celebration took place after
OL,12,Fthe couple had a legal ceremony in
OL,13,FSydney, where Mel C's "something
OL,14,Fborrowed" came from Posh Spice's own
OL,15,Fwardrobe, which inspired the dress for
OL,16,Fthe big day.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@^O]uD@WOUvD@IO]
