OL,3,CSpice Girl Mel C ties the knot in
OL,4,C'stunning' Cumbria wedding
OL,6,FChisolm added: "Victoria was so
OL,7,Fexcited about being able to do this
OL,8,Ffor me, and having her and (daughter)
OL,9,FScarlett there every step of the way
OL,10,Fhas been very special. Plus, I just
OL,11,Flove her clothes."
OL,13,FSpeaking about Dingwall, she added:
OL,14,F"The spark was immediate.
OL,16,F"I was 49 when I met Chris and I was
OL,17,Fin a really good place. We had a date
OL,18,Fin Australia, and it's been difficult
OL,19,Fto separate us ever since."
